ITALY: Italy July oil product consumption rises 2.6 pct.Italy July oil product consumption rises 2.6 pct.Italian oil product consumption rose 2.6 percent in July to 8.0 million tonnes compared with July 1995, according to data from trade group Unione Petrolifera.    Category	   July 1996 (million tonnes)  Change vs 1995    Total				8.000		  +2.6 pct    Total gasoline		   1.600		  +5.5 pct    Total gas oil		    1.400		  +5.9 pct    Total fuel oil		   1.860		  -0.6 pct